// Man page for time
manDate="TIME(7)                          X Shell Manual                          TIME(7)

<b>NAME</b>
    time - Display current time and date
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>time</b>
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Print the current system time and date.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <b>time</b>
    Display current time and date"